Description: PHP library to read pages from existing PDF documents
 FPDI is a collection of PHP classes facilitating developers to read pages
 from existing PDF documents and use them as templates in FPDF or TCPDF.
 It supports importing pages from PDF 1.0 to 1.7 documents.
